ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.aspen_forest.description=A forest filled with tall yellow Aspen trees, wildflowers, and shrubs.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.lavender_fields.description=A flat serene biome filled with purple Jacaranda trees, Wisteria, and Lavender flowers.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.autumn_woods.description=Fall-like biome filled with red and yellow Maple trees, orange oak trees, and pumpkins.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.badlands.description=Hot and dry biome with red rock formations, cacti, and sparse vegetation, with dry oak trees scattering the landscape.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.prairie.description=Mostly flat biome with tall grass, Clovers, and a few oak trees.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.savanna.description=Hot and dry biome with Strata, tall grass, acacia, and Baobab trees.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.deciduous_forest.description=A dense forest filled with oak trees of various sizes, flowers, and other vegetation.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.pendula_birch_forest.description=A forest filled with tall white birch trees, bees, Daisy Petals, and bushes.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.boggy_swamplands.description=A wet and moist biome with dark water, tall grass, and various plants.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.pale_garden.description=The pale garden has recieved a slight makeover, allowing the trees to be taller, added pale bushes, and added a dense pale fog.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.forsaken_depths.description=A dark and eerie biome with fossils, forsaken oak trees, hanging lichen, lichen carpet, and whispering willows.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.chorus_forest.description=An end biome filled with chorus trees, Void Blossoms, Void Blossoms Bushes, and a unique lively, but still lonely atmosphere.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.velvium_expanses.description=A vibrant and colorful biome with Velvium trees, Velvium Vines, and Cobbled End Stone boulders.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.depraved_wetlands.description=Wet, swamp-like biome with giant mushroom trees and depraved vegetation.\n\n\n

