ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.trial_tower.description=A tall tower containing several levels of trial spawners to fight through to obtain the loot at the top.\n\nSpawns in: Forests, Pendula Birch Forests, Mystic Roofed Forest, Prairie Plains, Desert, Mesa, Coniferous Forest\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.goblin_hut.description=Homes of Goblins, spawning up to several at a time.\n\nSpawns within the Mystic Roofed Forest.\n\n\n
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.ruined_altars.description=Old, abandonded altars that served an unknown purpose. Now dilapidated, and forgotten due to age.\n\nSpawns in: Forests, Taigas, and Mystic Roofed Forests.\n\n\n

