ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.sulfur_ore.description=A common ore found in the Overworld. It can be smelted into Sulfur, which is used for crafting gunpowder or as a fuel source.
ui.biomes_beyond.wiki.tungsten_ore.description=A rare ore found anywhere in the Overworld and in The End with a triangular distribution, between levels 16 through -64 in the overworld, and on the lower levels of end islands.\n\nSmelting produces Tungsten Ingots, which are used for crafting durable tools and armor.

